# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug
target

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
# Contains mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# RustRover
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
#.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Self-signed benchmark certs generated by xtask/docker/gen-certs.sh
# (issue #3 / docs/decisions/0001-clickhouse-client.md TLS scenario)
xtask/docker/certs/

# pulsus-write's writer core (issue #9): the default poison/uncertain
# spool directory, relative to the process (or test binary's) working
# directory, per `writer::config::WriterRuntime`'s documented constant.
/spool/
crates/pulsus-write/spool/

# Helm chart pytest-bdd suite (issue #38): kubeconfig for the session-scoped
# Kind cluster fixture, plus normal Python bytecode caches.
deploy/charts/pulsusdb/tests/bdd/.kubeconfig-*
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
